---
title: Pork Schnitzels & Cheesy Garlic Sauce with Rosemary Roasted Potatoes
description: We've turbo-charged schnitzel night! Special additions like a too-good-to-be-true cheesy garlic sauce, rosemary on the golden chunks of potato and a robust salad are what it's all about. Happy days indeed!
